LAST-MODIFIED:20260204T172550Z
UID:10002541-1776542400-1776553200@bigeasypetaluma.com
SUMMARY:The Big Easy Presents: Studio 54 Revisited
DESCRIPTION:STUDIO 54 Revisited: Marin County’s ultimate disco dance experience returns on Saturday\, April 18th at The Big Easy (Petaluma). Studio 54 Revisited brings live energy and groove with the greatest dance hits from the ’70s and beyond. You will hear classics from Chic\, KC and the Sunshine Band\, Earth\, Wind & Fire\, Kool & the Gang\, the Jackson 5\, Prince\, and many more songs that keep feet moving and hearts smiling. \n(Featuring professional Bay Area players who know how to turn a night into a celebration. Angie Maserati leads with dynamic vocals\, supported by Russ Gold on drums\, Aaron Chioino on guitar\, Tom Griesser on sax\, Geoff Vaughan on bass\, and Mickey Wray on keyboards. This group transforms timeless tunes into a live party that makes the crowd feel like they’ve stepped into the dance floor of a legendary disco.) \nCome dressed in your best 70s style to make the night even more immersive. Think wide collars\, bold patterns\, platform shoes and glitter. Get ready to boogie\, sweat\, and relive the magic of the disco era as Studio 54 Revisited delivers a set built for dancing and joy.
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/the-big-easy-presents-studio-54-revisited/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
CATEGORIES:Dance Ensemble
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/AEF1C7D5-AF0E-4319-9D14-E6AD602CFED1.jpeg
END:VEVENT
