SUMMARY:Feather & Flow: Burlesque & Live Music
DESCRIPTION:We’re back! Thotty McNaughty presents an evening of classic Live Jazz From Award-Winning Cabaret Chanteuse Coco Lamarr. In 2021\, Coco was awarded Best Vocalist and Best Film at the Hollywood & Southern California Burlesque Film Festival. In July 2024\, Coco won first place at The Battle of The Ballads singing competition at Juliet Cocktail Room inside the Venetian Casino & Resort. And in 2025\, she launched The Winehouse Revival\, a soul-soaked\, immersive tribute show celebrating the music and legacy of Amy Winehouse\, which has quickly become a highlight of California’s live music and cabaret scene. \nCoco will be backed by LBZ and band. LaiddBackZach (LBZ)\, is a North Bay/Bay Area R&B\, Hip-Hop\, Funk\, & Soul artist known for energetic shows with his band\, often performing in Sonoma County venues like the Luther Burbank Center for the Arts\, The California Theater\, The Big Easy and breweries\, blending songwriting with funk and soul grooves. You will also enjoy orginal pieces from LBZ and his band intermixed with Coco’s jazz covers and timeless Burlesque starring Rebel Rose\, Alotta Boutte\, Thotty McNaughty\, Montana Skye\, Kim\, and Velvet Thorn. \nThis is a one of a kind experience you will not want to miss! There is limited front row seating available and all other seating is General Admission.
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/feather-flow-burlesque-live-music/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Feather-Flow-everyone-5-x-7-in.png
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR